trans-unit.source: During execution a workflow in [!INCLUDE[netfx_current_short](../../../includes/netfx-current-short-md.md)] raises tracking events as it moves through various stages in its lifetime.
The host can subscribe to these events and keep updated on the status of the workflowâ€™s progress during its lifetime.
The tracking events raised are discussed in this section.
